taxi.model

Class Taxi

  • java.lang.Object
    • taxi.model.Taxi

  • @Entity
public class Taxi
extends java.lang.Object
    The Taxi class implements all taxis using the taxi service.

    Every taxi has a list of requests received, since it can receive several requests It also has:

    • carModel,
    • carType,
    • licensePlate,
    • carModelDate,
    • locationLat,
    • locationLon,
    • status,

    Since:
    Academic Year 2016-2017
    Author:
    Team 4

        Parameters:
        carModel - car model of the taxi, type String
        carType - car type of the taxi, type String
        licensePlate - license plate of the taxi, type String
        carModelDate - production date of the taxi, type String
        locationLat - latitude of the taxi, type double
        locationLon - longtitude of the taxi, type double
